le]]\n| align=center rowspan=2| [[1930 FIFA World Cup Group 1#Argentina vs Chile|3\u20131]]\n| rowspan=5|\n*[[1930 FIFA World Cup|1930]] vs [[1930 FIFA World Cup Group 1#Argentina vs Mexico|Mexico]] (3)\n| align=center rowspan=5| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://talksport.com/football/world-cups-most-iconic-players-1930-top-scorer-guillermo-stabile-180430280978 |title=The World Cup's most iconic players: 1930 top scorer Guillermo Stabile |publisher=talkSPORT.com |date=2018-04-30 |accessdate=2018-05-21}}</ref><!-- <ref>{{cite web |last=Formica |first=Federico |url=http://www.serieaddicted.com/article/serie-a-stars-in-the-world-cup_1930_guillermo-stabile-and-luis-monti.php |title=Serie A stars in the World Cup, 1930 \u2014 Guillermo Stabile and Luis Monti |publisher=SerieAddicted.com |date=2014-04-05 |accessdate=2014-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140720212953/http://www.serieaddicted.com/article/serie-a-stars-in-the-world-cup_1930_guillermo-stabile-and-luis-monti.php |archive-date=2014-07-20 |url-status=dead }}</ref> -->\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| 5\n| {{success|'''2'''\u20130}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| 6\n| rowspan=2| {{dts|1930|7|26|format=dmy}}\n| {{success|'''3'''\u20130}}\n| rowspan=2| [[United States men's national soccer team|United States]]\n| align=center rowspan=2| [[1930 FIFA World Cup knockout stage#Argentina vs United States|6\u20131]]\n| rowspan=2| [[1930 FIFA World Cup|1930, Uruguay]] <br> [[1930 FIFA World Cup#Semi-finals 2|Semi-final]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| 7\n| {{success|'''6'''\u20130}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=4| 8\n| {{dts|1930|7|30|format=dmy}}\n| {{success|'''2'''\u20131}}\n| [[Uruguay national football team|Uruguay]]\n| align=center|[[1930 FIFA World Cup Final|2\u20134]]\n| [[1930 FIFA World Cup|1930, Uruguay]] <br> [[1930 FIFA World Cup#Final 2|Final]]\n|-\n| {{dts|1938|6|19|format=dmy}}\n| [[Le\u00f4nidas]]\n| {{fb|BRA|1889}}\n| {{maybe|'''3'''\u20132}}\n| [[Sweden national football team|Sweden]]\n| align=center| [[1938 FIFA World C