/xbox-360/best-xbox-360-game-of-the-year.html |title=Best Xbox 360 Game of the Year 2010 - Mass Effect 2 - Xbox 360 |work=[[IGN]] |publisher=[[Ziff Davis]] |accessdate=April 9, 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131217221654/http://au.bestof.ign.com/2010/xbox-360/best-xbox-360-game-of-the-year.html |archivedate=December 17, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n|Funniest Game {{small|(PlayStation 3) (''[[Red Dead Redemption: Undead Nightmare|Undead Nightmare]]'')}}\n|{{nominated}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.spike.com/articles/ka13nu/video-game-awards-video-game-awards-2010-winners/ps3/funniest-game.html |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130615202629/http://www.spike.com/articles/ka13nu/video-game-awards-video-game-awards-2010-winners/ps3/funniest-game.html |url-status=dead |archive-date=June 15, 2013 |title=Funniest Game 2010 - Costume Quest - PS3 |work=[[IGN]] |publisher=[[Ziff Davis]] |accessdate=April 9, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n|Coolest Atmosphere {{small|(PlayStation 3)}}\n|{{nominated}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://au.bestof.ign.com/2010/ps3/coolest-atmosphere.html |title=Coolest Atmosphere 2010 - Castlevania: Lord of Shadows - PS3 |work=[[IGN]] |publisher=[[Ziff Davis]] |accessdate=April 9, 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120404180043/http://au.bestof.ign.com/2010/ps3/coolest-atmosphere.html |archivedate=April 4, 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n|Most Addictive Game {{small|(PlayStation 3)}}\n|{{nominated}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://au.bestof.ign.com/2010/ps3/most-addictive-game.html |title=Most Addictive Game 2010 - Pac-Man Championship Edition DX - PS3 |work=[[IGN]] |publisher=[[Ziff Davis]] |accessdate=April 9, 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120404180107/http://au.bestof.ign.com/2010/ps3/most-addictive-game.html |archivedate=April 4, 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n|Best Visuals {{small|(PlayStation 3)}}\n|{{nominated}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web |