]] |accessdate=April 9, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n|Overall Game of the Year\n|{{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://au.gamespy.com/articles/114/1141516p9.html |title=GameSpy: Game of the Year 2010 - Page 9 |publisher=[[GameSpy]] |accessdate=April 9, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"12\"|[[Spike (TV network)|Spike]] [[VGX (award show)|Video Game Awards]] [[VGX (award show)#2010 Awards|2010]]\n|Game of the Year\n|{{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"6\"|<ref name=\"spike vgas\"/>\n|-\n|Best Song in a Game {{small|(\"Far Away\" by [[Jos\u00e9 Gonz\u00e1lez (singer)|Jos\u00e9 Gonz\u00e1lez]])}}\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|Best Original Score\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|Best DLC {{small|(''[[Red Dead Redemption: Undead Nightmare|Undead Nightmare]]'')}}\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|Best Original Game\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|Best Zombie Game {{small|(''[[Red Dead Redemption: Undead Nightmare|Undead Nightmare]]'')}}\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|Studio of the Year {{small|([[Rockstar San Diego]])}}\n|{{nominated}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"6\"|<ref name=\"spike nominees\">{{cite web |url=http://www.destructoid.com/nominees-for-spike-video-game-awards-2010-revealed-187945.phtml |title=Nominees for Spike Video Game Awards 2010 revealed |website=[[Destructoid]] |date=November 17, 2010 |accessdate=April 9, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n|Character of the Year {{small|([[List of Red Dead Redemption characters#John Marston|John Marston]])}}\n|{{nominated}}\n|-\n|Best PS3 Game\n|{{nominated}}\n|-\n|Best Action Adventure Game\n|{{nominated}}\n|-\n|Best Graphics\n|{{nominated}}\n|-\n|Best Performance by a Human Male {{small|([[Rob Wiethoff]] as [[List of Red Dead Redemption characters#John Marston|John Marston]])}}\n|{{nominated}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"24\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|2011\n|rowspan=\"8\"|14th Annual [[Academy of Interactive Arts & Sciences|D.I.C.E. Awards]]\n|Action Game of the Year\n|{{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"8\"|<ref name=\"AIAS nominees and winners\">{{cite web |acce